    <p>She was quite frail but she had a good ap­petite.</p>
    <p>MR STEPHEN LEE, Madam Lily Loh’s prop­erty agent, on his last in­ter­ac­tion with her about five years ago. He de­scribed her as a very pri­vate per­son who was al­ways alone.</p>
    <p>UN­WILL­ING TO RE­CEIVE VIS­I­TORS</p>
    <p>If you are not re­cep­tive, there is a limit to what oth­ers can do (to help you).</p>
    <p>MR LIM BIOW CHUAN, Mount­bat­ten MP, who tried to help Madam Loh two years ago by alert­ing the po­lice and a so­cial worker, af­ter be­ing con­tacted by the condo’s man­age­ment. He said Madam Loh told the so­cial worker she was all right.</p>


